dashboardItems.text:
For a more accurate and timely dropout rate during a large scale up of two-dose vaccinations, the dashboards do not show gross totals first dose and last doses provided each reporting period. Instead, the dropout rate is calculated using a discrete time boundary between enrollment and final dose.

For COVAX1: 10 days
For COVAX2: 21 days
For COVAX 3: 28 days
